/awf
/dist
*.test
*.out

!.claude/
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock

# awf renders a CLAUDE.md @AGENTS.md bridge at the repo root (ADR-0016);
# negate the user's global CLAUDE.md ignore so the rendered artifact commits.
!CLAUDE.md

# awf dogfoods a cursor adapter (ADR-0037); negate any global .cursor ignore so
# the rendered .cursor/ tree commits and is drift-checked.
!.cursor/

# Keep every dogfooded adapter output visible despite common global ignores.
!.agents/
!.codex/
!.github/
!.gemini/
!.pi/
.pi/awf-subagents.local.json
!GEMINI.md
